      <segment state="final">
        <source>eMule #</source>
        <target>eMule 支持 #</target>
      </segment>
    </unit>
    <unit id="5a71a2b3-8762-48aa-b45b-2db5b02d0e08">
      <notes>
        <note appliesTo="source">line: 4</note>
        <note appliesTo="source">prefix: *	</note>
      </notes>
      <segment state="final">
        <source>Authors: Noelia, Chris, Alberto.</source>
        <target>作者： Noelia、Chris、Alberto。</target>
      </segment>
    </unit>
    <unit id="1e4fe4b6-1381-4732-aff8-1bbf2211db75">
      <notes>
        <note appliesTo="source">line: 6</note>
      </notes>
      <segment state="final">
        <source>This add-on helps to improve accessibility of eMule with nVDA.</source>
        <target>此插件有助于提高 eMule 与 NVDA 的可访问性。</target>
      </segment>
    </unit>
    <unit id="8d6cf124-9912-4cab-afba-81eefa1613a1">
      <notes>
        <note appliesTo="source">line: 7</note>
      </notes>
      <segment state="final">
        <source>It also provides additional keyboard commands for moving in different windows and gives Useful information about eMule.</source>
        <target>它还提供了用于在不同窗口中移动的其他键盘命令，并提供了有关eMule的有用信息。</target>
      </segment>
    </unit>
    <unit id="f345ab72-f196-466e-bec8-24ee7333eb5f">
      <notes>
        <note appliesTo="source">line: 9</note>
      </notes>
      <segment state="final">
        <source>It's based on the eMuleNVDASupport add-on, developed by the same author. You should uninstall that old add-on to use this one, since both have common keystrokes and features.</source>
        <target>当前插件基于同一作者开发的eMuleNVDASupport插件。您应该卸载该旧插件以使用此插件，因为两者都有共同的按键和功能。</target>
      </segment>
    </unit>
    <unit id="bf657429-acda-46eb-9094-059697f5e59e">
      <notes>
        <note appliesTo="source">line: 11</note>
      </notes>
      <segment state="final">
        <source>Tested on [eMule][1] 0.50a and 70b.</source>
        <target>已在[eMule][1] 0.50a 和 70b 上测试。</target>
      </segment>
    </unit>
    <unit id="76bdc5b1-30ae-4362-bfd9-b601c194e236">
      <notes>
        <note appliesTo="source">line: 13</note>
        <note appliesTo="source">prefix: ## </note>
      </notes>
      <segment state="final">
        <source>Key Commands: ##</source>
        <target>快捷键: ##</target>
      </segment>
    </unit>
    <unit id="017a9db7-1e92-4057-924f-54890be7374c">
      <notes>
        <note appliesTo="source">line: 15</note>
        <note appliesTo="source">prefix: *	</note>
      </notes>
      <segment state="final">
        <source>control+shift+h: Moves focus and mouse to main toolbar.</source>
        <target>control+shift+h： 移动鼠标和焦点到”主工具栏。</target>
      </segment>
    </unit>
    <unit id="8ada21f4-bcee-4467-95f5-ab067f021507">
      <notes>
        <note appliesTo="source">line: 16</note>
        <note appliesTo="source">prefix: *	</note>
      </notes>
      <segment state="final">
        <source>control+shift+t: Reads the current window.</source>
        <target>control+shift+t: 朗读当前窗口。</target>
      </segment>
    </unit>
    <unit id="10c65fcd-84ef-4532-ab28-07746e447da6">
      <notes>
        <note appliesTo="source">line: 17</note>
        <note appliesTo="source">prefix: *	</note>
      </notes>
      <segment state="final">
        <source>control+shift+n: Moves the focus to the Name field in the Find window.</source>
        <target>control+shift+n： 移动焦点到“查找”窗口的“名称”编辑区。</target>
      </segment>
    </unit>
    <unit id="ab29215f-6306-44b4-b680-7d0a2f12a03d">
      <notes>
        <note appliesTo="source">line: 18</note>
        <note appliesTo="source">prefix: *	</note>
      </notes>
      <segment state="final">
        <source>control+shift+p: In the Search window, moves focus and mouse to the list of search parameters, or edit field options.</source>
        <target>control+shift+p： 切换焦点和鼠标到“搜索”窗口的搜索参数列表和编辑区选项。</target>
      </segment>
    </unit>
    <unit id="22992bbc-74a6-48a0-a6fd-a85850c66f3a">
      <notes>
        <note appliesTo="source">line: 19</note>
        <note appliesTo="source">prefix: *	</note>
      </notes>
      <segment state="final">
        <source>control+shift+b: Move the focus to the list in the current window. For example usable in the Search window, downloads in Transfer window, etc.</source>
        <target>control + shift + b：将焦点移动到当前窗口的列表中。例如，可在“搜索”窗口中使用，在“传输”窗口中下载等。</target>
      </segment>
    </unit>
    <unit id="6661b0ee-e85d-4204-857b-8b092bfa32b8">
      <notes>
        <note appliesTo="source">line: 20</note>
        <note appliesTo="source">prefix: *	</note>
      </notes>
      <segment state="final">
        <source>control+shift+o: Move the focus to read-only edit boxes in the current window. For example the IRC received messages, available Servers, etc.</source>
        <target>control + shift + o：将焦点移动到当前窗口中的只读编辑框。例如，IRC收到消息，可用服务器等。</target>
      </segment>
    </unit>
    <unit id="39e8f840-affc-48b7-aecb-a0a7c1958430">
      <notes>
        <note appliesTo="source">line: 21</note>
        <note appliesTo="source">prefix: *	</note>
      </notes>
      <segment state="final">
        <source>control+NVDA+f: If the caret is located in a read only edit box, opens a find dialog to use the commands for searching text available in NVDA.</source>
        <target>control + NVDA + f：如果插入符号位于只读编辑框中，则打开查找对话框以使用命令搜索NVDA中可用的文本。</target>
      </segment>
    </unit>
    <unit id="ad99d8db-8069-4655-8198-92b6f16be9cd">
      <notes>
        <note appliesTo="source">line: 22</note>
        <note appliesTo="source">prefix: *	</note>
      </notes>
      <segment state="final">
        <source>control+shift+l: Moves the navigator object and mouse to the headers of the current list.</source>
        <target>control+shift+l： 移动鼠标和浏览对象到当前列表的表头。</target>
      </segment>
    </unit>
    <unit id="0e1fadec-c707-42d6-ad3a-c229cfdf0d76">
      <notes>
        <note appliesTo="source">line: 23</note>
        <note appliesTo="source">prefix: *	</note>
      </notes>
      <segment state="final">
        <source>control+shift+q: Reads the first object in the status bar; provides information about recent activity.</source>
        <target>control+shift+q： 朗读状态栏的第一个对象，提供最近一次活动的信息。</target>
      </segment>
    </unit>
    <unit id="5095c70a-12b3-4d99-bd7c-b9c3797f765d">
      <notes>
        <note appliesTo="source">line: 24</note>
        <note appliesTo="source">prefix: *	</note>
      </notes>
      <segment state="final">
        <source>control+shift+w: Reads the second object of the status bar; contains information about files and users on the current server.</source>
        <target>control+shift+w： 朗读状态栏的第二个对象，提供当前服务器的用户和文件的数目信息。</target>
      </segment>
    </unit>
    <unit id="0e9da299-bdd2-4004-a7d8-b7cb6f0803a2">
      <notes>
        <note appliesTo="source">line: 25</note>
        <note appliesTo="source">prefix: *	</note>
      </notes>
      <segment state="final">
        <source>control+shift+e: Reads the third object of the status bar; useful to know the UpLoad/DownLoad speed.</source>
        <target>control+shift+e： 朗读状态栏的第三个对象，常用来了解上传和下载速度。</target>
      </segment>
    </unit>
    <unit id="97a59d08-a847-4379-8b0b-2a49faa8dfc1">
      <notes>
        <note appliesTo="source">line: 26</note>
        <note appliesTo="source">prefix: *	</note>
      </notes>
      <segment state="final">
        <source>control+shift+r: Reads The fourth object of the status bar; reports on connecting of eD2K and Kad network.</source>
        <target>control+shift+r： 朗读状态栏的第四个对象，关于 eD2K 和 Kad 网络连接的信息。</target>
      </segment>
    </unit>
    <unit id="d8d260eb-0cc7-462b-8797-0fdb08785c36">
      <notes>
        <note appliesTo="source">line: 27</note>
        <note appliesTo="source">prefix: * </note>
      </notes>
      <segment state="final">
        <source>Not assigned: Toggles the usage of an alternative approach to read sliders.</source>
        <target>未分配： 启用或禁用滑块控件的备选朗读方案。</target>
      </segment>
    </unit>
    <unit id="ad34c9e5-b5aa-4313-9342-4c5719de6ce4">
      <notes>
        <note appliesTo="source">line: 29</note>
        <note appliesTo="source">prefix: ## </note>
      </notes>
      <segment state="final">
        <source>Managing columns. ##</source>
        <target>管理列。 ##</target>
      </segment>
    </unit>
    <unit id="597b00de-d1ea-4de8-9f5b-8d716c03456c">
      <notes>
        <note appliesTo="source">line: 31</note>
      </notes>
      <segment state="final">
        <source>When within a list, you can move the caret between the rows and columns using alt+control+ Arrows.</source>
        <target>在一个列表内，您可以使用 CTRL加ALT家光标键 在列表的行列之间进行浏览。</target>
      </segment>
    </unit>
    <unit id="ca114d28-c85c-46da-b600-563c04de8c36">
      <notes>
        <note appliesTo="source">line: 32</note>
      </notes>
      <segment state="final">
        <source>In this Add-on the following key commands are also available:</source>
        <target>在此插件，下面的按键也是可用的：</target>
      </segment>
